## 1ï¸âƒ£1ï¸âƒ£ â€œExplain fast-forward vs merge commit.â€

### Strong answer:

> â€œFast-forward moves the branch pointer forward without a merge commit when histories havenâ€™t diverged.â€

---

## 1ï¸âƒ£2ï¸âƒ£ â€œHow do you fix a wrong remote URL?â€

```bash
